      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, peel and chop the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>and <strong>potatoes</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into discs</p><p>Add the<strong> carrot discs </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potatoes </strong>(the sweet potato will be added later) to the pan and cook for 4-5 min until slightly softened</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p>",
