      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed coconut </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
