            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the carrot and potatoes have slightly softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with the <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground allspice </strong>and the <strong>bay leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong></p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), give everything a good mix up and cook for a further 1 min until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1649172709828-x200.jpg",
