            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped sweet potato </strong>to the pan with the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the sweet potato is fork-tender and the sauce has thickened slightly</p>",
