      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweet potato is tender, wash the <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> spinach</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for a final 2 min or until the spinach is wilted – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>sweet potato & carrot Ital-style stew</strong></p>",
