    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the spinach is wilting, add the <strong>roti </strong>to a plate and pop in the<strong> microwave</strong> for 20 secs on high or until warmed</p><p>Tip: For a little extra indulgence, spread the hot roti with<strong> </strong>butter alternative once it's out of the microwave</p>",
