      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy sweet potato & carrot Ital-style stew </strong>in bowls with the <strong>warmed roti </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
